Important Constraints
Build only the frontend foundation.
Do not connect a backend.
Do not connect Gemini API.
Do not implement machine learning.
Do not implement ticket classification logic.
Do not implement sentiment analysis logic.
Do not implement knowledge retrieval.
Do not add unnecessary features.
Use mock placeholder content where required.
Final Verification
Before finishing:
Verify every sidebar navigation item.
Verify every page opens correctly.
Verify there are no blank pages.
Verify there are no broken routes.
Verify there are no visible frontend errors.
Verify the mobile sidebar works.
Do not proceed to advanced features.
Stop after completing the frontend foundation.
